<BlogPost
  title="How to improve your AI coding assistant's output quality"
  description="Practical techniques for getting better code from Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot, and other AI coding tools. Covers project configs, structured prompting, conventions, and guardrails."
  date="April 10, 2026"
  readTime="11 min read"
